127. pransus, etc.: only a light breakfast, at about tWO, to stay his stomach till dinner‚ the hour of which was rather late with him. Cf. 1 1 3. The dinner hour varied, as with ηε, from say three o'clock till seven.

130. his: neuter, and depending as an ablative of manner on victu- rum.

131. quaestor: the lowest of the offices is put for them all. His reason for preferring the lowest is not clear. Perhaps it is one of his unexpected turns, coming in as a jest upon himself, as it were.
